      "date": "2014-12-26 19:47:10.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified-1\n\nBuild Failed \n \nhttps://build.hpdd.intel.com/job/lustre-reviews/29292/ : FAILURE",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
