    {
      "id": "aa014c220f9aaad7e28268a31cf9a44137d48a7e",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 117,
        "name": "Andreas Dilger",
        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2014-12-28 07:06:28.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\n(3 comments)\n\nSome minor style issues that could be fixed if patch needs to be refreshed for some reason. \n\nWhat happens with a new client if a 2.5 client tries \"mkdir -i\" on a master (2.7.0) server (i.e. sends RPC to the master/wrong MDT)?  Is the LASSERT() still there or was it removed in master? Does the MDT send the request to the right MDT?\n\nI was trying to figure out why the build failed, but I see this patch is based on v2.6.0 even though it is pushed on master. Unfortunately this has no hope to build on master. \n\nSince you have pushed a copy of this patch to b2_6 I will abandon this patch.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "d5683fa13a2c59d7cce533f1bcbb5c9441a740ac",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 12,
        "name": "wangdi",
        "email": "di.wang@intel.com",
        "username": "wangdi",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2014-12-28 18:59:52.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWhat happens with a new client if a 2.5 client tries \"mkdir -i\" on a master (2.7.0) server (i.e. sends RPC to the master/wrong MDT)? Is the LASSERT() still there or was it removed in master? Does the MDT send the request to the right MDT?\n\nHmm, the new server (>=2.6) should be able to deal with the request from the create request from the Old client, i.e. the master (or 2.6) MDT can create the remote directory whether it is from new client (sending to salve MDT) or from old client (sending to master MDT). I remember we did that test when 2.6 release. Unfortunately we did not try new client with old server.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "4fc4865fcc1b0e04a815aa93f0e5c23ee01d8da7",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 454,
        "name": "Artem Blagodarenko",
        "email": "ablagodarenko@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "ablagodarenko"
      },
      "date": "2014-12-29 09:03:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nYes, sure. I have uploaded the patch to master by mistake. Let's continue review in http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/13190/ Andreas, please, abandon this patch.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
